    <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6">
      Take your game beyond word knowledge. These strategy guides cover rack management, offensive and defensive play, 
      tile tracking, opening theory, midgame control, endgame techniques, and advanced tactics like parallel plays and 
      bingo stems. Each article is built for players ready to compete at a higher level.
    </p>

    <!-- Stat Strip: Category Overview -->
    <div class="not-prose my-8 p-4 rounded-xl border border-emerald-500/30 bg-emerald-950/10">
