    <!-- Hero Card #1: Rack Management -->
    <div class="not-prose my-8 p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-emerald-500/50 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-950/30 to-teal-950/20 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-3 right-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-500/70">🏆 #1 Skill to Master</div>
      <p class="text-2xl font-black text-white tracking-wider mb-2">RACK MANAGEMENT</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-emerald-300 font-semibold mb-3">The single biggest differentiator between casual and competitive players</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">What you keep on your rack after each play determines your future options. Tournament players don't just find the highest-scoring word — they choose the play that scores well AND leaves the best remaining tiles. A balanced rack with common letters (S, E, R, A, N, T) plus a blank is the gateway to consistent bingos.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero Card #2: Board Control -->
